351
00:15:07,369 --> 00:15:08,928
you didn't even graduate high school,

352
00:15:08,929 --> 00:15:10,838
and your only references are

353
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:13,178
photographers and aging rock stars.

354
00:15:13,295 --> 00:15:16,455
