356
00:15:20,074 --> 00:15:21,643
So now what am I supposed to do?

357
00:15:21,864 --> 00:15:24,767
Well, you could start planning
that august vacation.

358
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:34,344
<i>Gabrielle Solis was depressed,</i>

359
