black sheath dress would
go perfect with it.

368
00:15:54,695 --> 00:15:55,733
Mm.

369
00:15:56,995 --> 00:15:58,682
Look at those over-the-knee boots!

370
00:15:59,757 --> 00:16:01,194
Okay. Who am I kidding?

371
00:16:01,337 --> 00:16:03,402
Get me a double cappuccino
and a muscular stock boy.

372
