478
00:20:55,532 --> 00:20:58,082
You bought... one boot?

479
00:20:58,147 --> 00:21:00,025
Yep. 'Cause I'm frugal.

480
00:21:00,125 --> 00:21:02,271
One day I'll buy the other one.

481
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,877
