with your credit card.

484
00:21:09,992 --> 00:21:12,264
Huh. Maybe it was stolen.

485
00:21:12,371 --> 00:21:13,469
Yeah.

486
00:21:13,567 --> 00:21:17,848
By a size 0 with
incredibly expensive taste.

487
00:21:17,992 --> 00:21:19,480
What is this shopping bag
doing under the bed?

488
00:21:19,573 --> 00:21:22,077
I bought a gift for a woman

489
00:21:22,479 --> 00:21:25,516
