493
00:21:34,505 --> 00:21:36,813
Can't take it back.
Can't take it back now.

494
00:21:36,847 --> 00:21:37,782
See? It's all...

495
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:39,556
Stop. Stop. Stop. Stop. Stop!

496
00:21:40,102 --> 00:21:42,954
